// Personal signing — copy this file to "Local.xcconfig" (same folder) and fill
// in your own values. Local.xcconfig is gitignored, so your team id and bundle
// ids are never committed.
//
// The App Group and the broadcast extension id are derived from the app bundle
// id at runtime / via build-setting expansion, so changing the bundle id below
// is all you need — nothing else has to be edited.

// DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = YOURTEAMID
// LUMA_BUNDLE_ID_APP = com.example.Luma
// LUMA_BUNDLE_ID_TESTS = com.example.LumaTests
// LUMA_BUNDLE_ID_EXTENSION = com.example.Luma.BroadcastExtension
